WEBVTT

00:03:59.440 --> 00:04:00.896
suspension bridges.

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:03.200
And the opportunity
for variety is enormous.

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:07.616
Engineers have a fantastic scope
for innovation and ingenuity

00:04:07.640 --> 00:04:10.200
and developing different forms
around these types.

00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:17.216
But technological change
happens relatively slowly in my world,

00:04:17.240 --> 00:04:18.456
believe it or not,

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:23.016
compared to the changes
that happen in mobile phone technology

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:25.376
and computers and digital
technologies and so on.

00:04:25.400 --> 00:04:27.656
In our world of construction,

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:30.240
the changes seem positively glacial.